  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embark on an adrenaline-fueled adventure with \"Satan Moans\"? In this horror-packed and thrilling game, you'll explore the supernatural events that befall a teenager returning home in the dead of night. The focal point of the game will be to immerse players in disturbing and suspenseful details, creating a dark and eerie atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/bc3c3b555b275537b703f38e48a6b9cb.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/bc3c3b555b275537b703f38e48a6b9cb.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/bc3c3b555b275537b703f38e48a6b9cb.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/934a338a2056e5f92773fb5d29778932.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/934a338a2056e5f92773fb5d29778932.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/934a338a2056e5f92773fb5d29778932.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will face unsettling visuals and creatures' sounds and sudden appearances as they attempt to unravel the mystery behind the supernatural events haunting the house. In dark rooms, mysterious corridors, and chilling corners, players will venture into the depths of the house filled with mysteries. But beware, danger lurks around every corner, and every room holds a secret!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/7c0ace38374426f7b7fd0358a4a66fa5.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/7c0ace38374426f7b7fd0358a4a66fa5.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/7c0ace38374426f7b7fd0358a4a66fa5.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will quicken players' hearts with its disturbing and suspenseful visual elements. With tension-filled moments at every turn, this game will draw you into a world of horror. Remember, the only way to uncover the secrets hidden in the darkness is by solving puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/0d9f269b6797613b257c9103c1a8b9b3.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/0d9f269b6797613b257c9103c1a8b9b3.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/0d9f269b6797613b257c9103c1a8b9b3.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/543e40276aeabce1b5ddbe26bb8966a0.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/543e40276aeabce1b5ddbe26bb8966a0.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/543e40276aeabce1b5ddbe26bb8966a0.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Satan Moans\" is the perfect choice for horror and thriller enthusiasts. Its spine-chilling story and challenging puzzles will captivate you and plunge you into a suspenseful adventure. Are you ready to explore the supernatural events unfolding in a dark and eerie house?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features of the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The genre of \"Walking Simulator\";</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tense atmosphere;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 3D surround sound;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic graphics;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Sudden Scary Sounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Disturbing editor images.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to embark on an adrenaline-fueled adventure with \"Satan Moans\"? In this horror-packed and thrilling game, you'll explore the supernatural events that befall a teenager returning home in the dead of night. The focal point of the game will be to immerse players in disturbing and suspenseful details, creating a dark and eerie atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/bc3c3b555b275537b703f38e48a6b9cb.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/bc3c3b555b275537b703f38e48a6b9cb.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/bc3c3b555b275537b703f38e48a6b9cb.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/934a338a2056e5f92773fb5d29778932.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/934a338a2056e5f92773fb5d29778932.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/934a338a2056e5f92773fb5d29778932.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will face unsettling visuals and creatures' sounds and sudden appearances as they attempt to unravel the mystery behind the supernatural events haunting the house. In dark rooms, mysterious corridors, and chilling corners, players will venture into the depths of the house filled with mysteries. But beware, danger lurks around every corner, and every room holds a secret!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/7c0ace38374426f7b7fd0358a4a66fa5.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/7c0ace38374426f7b7fd0358a4a66fa5.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/7c0ace38374426f7b7fd0358a4a66fa5.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will quicken players' hearts with its disturbing and suspenseful visual elements. With tension-filled moments at every turn, this game will draw you into a world of horror. Remember, the only way to uncover the secrets hidden in the darkness is by solving puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/0d9f269b6797613b257c9103c1a8b9b3.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/0d9f269b6797613b257c9103c1a8b9b3.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/0d9f269b6797613b257c9103c1a8b9b3.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/543e40276aeabce1b5ddbe26bb8966a0.poster.avif?t=1745414516\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/543e40276aeabce1b5ddbe26bb8966a0.webm?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000520/extras/543e40276aeabce1b5ddbe26bb8966a0.mp4?t=1745414516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Satan Moans\" is the perfect choice for horror and thriller enthusiasts. Its spine-chilling story and challenging puzzles will captivate you and plunge you into a suspenseful adventure. Are you ready to explore the supernatural events unfolding in a dark and eerie house?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features of the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The genre of \"Walking Simulator\";</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Tense atmosphere;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 3D surround sound;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Realistic graphics;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Sudden Scary Sounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Disturbing editor images.</p>",
